{"tid":832601,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人根本唔想拍拖？","createTime":"2018-09-23T01:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T02:57:19.000Z","uid":208270,"like":160,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"38478818025d158ee39bcd8d166168ba095eab92","tid":832601,"uid":208270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T01:41:02.000Z","msg":"但不斷有人approach，其實對於我呢啲無意發展任何關係嘅人真係好困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我通常都唔會覆，好彩遇到嘅都唔會死纏爛打，咁我就可以抖下氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人愈大，我連朋友都唔想再識，覺得自己嘅幾個好朋友已夠我一生<br />\n依家返工識人基本上講兩句已經知做唔做到朋友/叫做講到嘢，但有啲人太aggressive，我連嘢都唔想同佢地講，唔想俾任何機會人接觸我，我會唔會好怪？<br />\n<br />\n利申：A0"},{"pid":"79780589814e4d88daee8ef4a916ed5349224b35","tid":832601,"uid":64925,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T01:46:55.000Z","msg":"老友真係4、5個就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍唔拍拖冇咩所謂 但唔會主動去爭取<br />\n放假就成日留係屋企睇youtube movies or動畫就算<br />\n如果d老友同時得閒咪出黎傾下計 遊下車河咁<br />\n一樣a0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bcaff680927d65c4638180052970b425a24ea6","tid":832601,"uid":160853,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T01:47:35.000Z","msg":"你唔係唔想拍拖 只係你愛的人不愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0148d3b38d7a77f19c64e3677789c984b340a6","tid":832601,"uid":208270,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"79780589814e4d88daee8ef4a916ed5349224b35","tid":832601,"uid":64925,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T01:46:55.000Z","msg":"老友真係4、5個就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍唔拍拖冇咩所謂 但唔會主動去爭取<br />\n放假就成日留係屋企睇youtube movies or動畫就算<br />\n如果d老友同時得閒咪出黎傾下計 遊下車河咁<br />\n一樣a0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T02:01:48