23T09:13:04.000Z","msg":"樓主係絲打???<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為如果依個post係巴打開一定俾人話毒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我反而係以前想拍<br />\n<br />\n人愈來愈大覺得拍拖有d煩<br />\n特別自己去左旅行之後,唔想俾人左右行程<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前溝過一個女仔佢同樓主一樣,都係好多人追,但佢唔想拍拖<br />\n其他追佢果d有靚仔有有錢仔"},{"pid":"890ec9d4542118d0f4b436510deeee12e9419108","tid":832601,"uid":204715,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"以前year 1,2拍拖 分左手 好快可以move on搵下一個<br />\n而家拍完 最少等返一年半載先會搵下一個<br />\n有對象approach 都會潛意識縮開<br />\n可能始終人大左 顧慮多啲<br />\n而且個人一忙起上黎 就唔會有心機諗呢啲 覺得嘥時間<br />\nKeep 住最好嘅朋友係身邊 同埋有屋企人係背後 對我而家黎講已經好足夠啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54894263be63d6608f3bd84e21b01ce5b16f1568","tid":832601,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:25:27.000Z","msg":"我想拍拖呀<br />\n但唔想做做牌個過程"},{"pid":"143245e1e660f67adf3129b1a417308ef62e8d5d","tid":832601,"uid":73555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"到有一日你身邊所有人都結晒婚生晒仔，而你重係一個人每日得返工同放工，你就唔會再咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af96c982609f9586fdf22acbebf507bc9ac8e2b","tid":832601,"uid":50310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:28:56.000Z","msg":"快啲囉返個.貞節牌坊啦！<br />\n要黎做乜喎！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c866eb8fe5774cf94d286d7f9356d98256cb4efb","tid":832601,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:35:30.000Z","msg":"條女係處咪拍囉!<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係處就一腳伸走佢!<br />\n<br />\n利申:9up!"},{"pid":"417c93337e98af91dcb75d5b034b3c31dc027491","tid":832601,"uid":199321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"843c43dc68d7b2bc1950c5b72024f3a9b7078a3c","tid":832601,"uid":176792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5fa1612b4aa0a6e7e29ef44a5932d0a5189baeba","tid":832601,"uid":181527,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"cited